{
  "stem": "3040.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they had to control that one wouldn't get soup twice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The soup was handed out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you came with your-- you had some kind of a container for the soup.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You came-- if you came too close to-- to the-- to the canister-- you know, too close, just too close-- he hit you over the head.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "What are you-- you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "If you were too far away, he dropped the soup on the floor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This was going on all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was the kapos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These-- they were handing out the soup.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if you were a little off, not so close enough, so instead of dropping the soup into your container, they dropped it on the floor.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It happened to me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It happened to a lot of people, because they-- they were finding ways to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] reduce you, you know, to-- to just-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] sometimes I'm very fluent and it comes to this and I'm missing words.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, this procedure was over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the afternoon, they chased us out of the barracks again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If it was nice weather outside, they left us stay inside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If it was nasty, they chased us out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And about 6:00, into the barracks again, and there was distribution of bread in the evening.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the morning was supposed to be the coffee, and then the soup, and then the bread.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So everybody got a slice of bread, like the Wonder Bread you have-- you see here in these packages.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Something of that kind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This-- one slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Black bread, something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We don't know what it was made of.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
